value.0: This Lathanderite priestess, of the rank of Dawngreeter, looks like she has come from a more urban setting, or perhaps an upper class.  She is still encouraging and kind, even if she has an air of nobility about her.  She wears the traditional rose quartz disc, which emanates a faint glow.

Value.value: No need for alarm, you will not fall from these window.
Welcome to the Shrine of Lathander.
The blessings of the Morning Lord be upon you!

value.0: A table fit for a king.
To the east, a dark tunnel which emerges from the mountain. To the west, brightly lit stairs that lead upward.
Even if it is night time, you sense a great deal of light on the other side of this door.
The gold carpet and blue walls indicate opulence as well as suggest a sun in the sky motif.
